769 [XmlRoot("Filter")]
770 public class SegmentationFilter
771 {
772 public SegmentationFilter()
773 {
774 CriteriaJoinOperator = "";
775 Criterias = [];
776 }
777 public SegmentationFilter(XmlElement xmlFilter)
778 {
779 CriteriaJoinOperator = xmlFilter.GetAttribute("CriteriaJoinOperator");
780 var critList = new List<SegmentationFilterCriteria>();
781 var filterCriteriasXML = xmlFilter.GetElementsByTagName("Criteria");
782 for (var i = 0; i < filterCriteriasXML.Count; i++)
783 {
784 var filterCriteriaXML = (XmlElement)filterCriteriasXML.Item(i);
785 var newCrit = new SegmentationFilterCriteria
786 {
787 Row = 0
788 };
789 if (filterCriteriaXML.GetAttribute("Row") != "")
790 {
791 newCrit.Row = Convert.ToInt32(filterCriteriaXML.GetAttribute("Row"));
792 }
793
794 newCrit.Field = filterCriteriaXML.GetAttribute("Field");
795 newCrit.Operation = filterCriteriaXML.GetAttribute("Operator");
796 newCrit.Value = filterCriteriaXML.GetAttribute("Value");
797 critList.Add(newCrit);
798 }
799
800 Criterias = critList;
801 }
802
803 public SegmentationFilter(string filter)
804 {

811 for (var i = 0; i < filterCriteriasXML.Count; i++)
812 {

903 public static class SegmentationFilterHelper
904 {
905 public static SegmentationFilter GenerateEqualFilter(string field, string value)
906 {
907 var filter = new SegmentationFilter()
908 {
909 CriteriaJoinOperator = "|",
910 Criterias = [
911 new() { Field = field, Operation = "Equal", Row = 0, Value = value},
912 new() { Field = field, Operation = "StartsWith", Row = 1, Value = value + ";"},
913 new() { Field = field, Operation = "EndsWith", Row = 2, Value = ";" + value},
914 new() { Field = field, Operation = "Contains", Row = 3, Value = ";" + value + ";" }
915 ]
916 };
917 return filter;
918 }
919
920 public static SegmentationFilter FormatFilter(this SegmentationFilter segmentationFilter, List<ContactGroupForMF> groups)
921 {
922 return segmentationFilter.CheckSegmentationFilterIntegrity() ? GenerateEmptyFilter() : segmentationFilter.FormatFilterBase(groups);
923 }
924
925 private static SegmentationFilter FormatFilterBase(this SegmentationFilter segmentationFilter, List<ContactGroupForMF> groups)
926 {
927 if (groups == null)
928 {
929 return segmentationFilter.ReplaceNumericJoinOperator()
930 .SetCriteriaJoinToNumeric()
931 .SetBlankCriteria()
932 .SetTagsField()
933 .SetDateFields()
934 .SetFilterCriteriasForNONEState()
935 .RemoveEmptyJoinOperationValue();
936 }
937 else
938 {
939 return segmentationFilter.ReplaceNumericJoinOperator()
940 .SetCriteriaJoinToNumeric()
941 .SetBlankCriteria()
942 .SetTagsField()
943 .SetDateFields()
944 .SetFilterCriteriasForNONEState()
945 .SetGroupFilter(groups)
946 .RemoveEmptyJoinOperationValue();
947 }
948 }

950 public static bool CheckSegmentationFilterIntegrity(this SegmentationFilter segmentationFilter)
951 {
952 return segmentationFilter.Criterias == null || segmentationFilter.Criterias.Count < 1 || string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator);
953 }
954
955 public static SegmentationFilter GenerateEmptyFilter()
956 {
957 return new SegmentationFilter
958 {
959 CriteriaJoinOperator = "(0)",
960 Criterias =
961 [
962 GenerateNoCriteriaFilter()
963 ]
964 };
965 }
966
967 public static SegmentationFilter SetGroupFilter(this SegmentationFilter segmentationFilter, List<ContactGroupForMF> groups, bool isThirdLevel = false)
968 {
969 if (groups.Count > 0)
970 {
971 var criterias = segmentationFilter.Criterias.Where(x => x.Field.Equals("groupname", StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase)).ToList();
972 foreach (var criteria in segmentationFilter.Criterias.Where(x => x.Field.Equals("groupname", StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase)).ToList())
973 {
974 var group = groups.GetGroupByName(criteria.Value);
975 if (group == null)
976 {
977 criteria.SetNoGroupFoundCriteria();
978 continue;
979 }
980
981 SegmentationFilter groupFilter = null;
982 if (group.Filter is null)
983 {
984 groupFilter = GenerateEmptyFilter();
985 }
986 else
987 {
988 groupFilter = group.Filter.Replace("Field=\"group\"", "Field=\"GroupName\"").DeserializeXML<SegmentationFilter>();
989 if (groupFilter.CheckSegmentationFilterIntegrity())
990 {
991 groupFilter = GenerateEmptyFilter();
992 }
993 }
994
995 _ = groupFilter.ReplaceNumericJoinOperator()
996 .SetCriteriaJoinToNumeric()
997 .SetBlankCriteria()
998 .SetTagsField()
999 .SetDateFields()
1000 .RemoveGroupCriteria(isThirdLevel)
1001 .SetGroupFilter(groups, true)
1002 .UpdateRowNumbers(segmentationFilter.GetHighestRow());
1003 segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator = segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator.ReplaceJoinOperatorValue(criteria.Row, groupFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator);
1004 segmentationFilter.Criterias.AddRange(groupFilter.Criterias);
1005 }
1006
1007 _ = segmentationFilter.Criterias.RemoveAll(x => x.Field.Equals("groupname", StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase));
1008 }
1009
1010 return segmentationFilter;
1011 }
1012
1013 public static SegmentationFilter SetFilterCriteriasForNONEState(this SegmentationFilter segmentationFilter)
1014 {
1015 var criteriasForAdd = new List<SegmentationFilterCriteria>();
1016 foreach (var criteria in segmentationFilter.Criterias.Where(x => x.Field.Equals("state", StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase) && x.Value.Equals("none", StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase)))
1017 {
1018 if (criteria.Operation.ToLower() is "equal" or "notequal")
1019 {
1020 int first = Math.Max(segmentationFilter.GetHighestRow(), criteriasForAdd.Select(x => x.Row).Append(0).Max() + 1), second = first + 1, third = first + 2;
1021
1022 criteriasForAdd.AddRange(new List<SegmentationFilterCriteria>
1023 {
1024 SegmentationFilterCriteria.GenerateFilterCriteria(criteria.Field, criteria.Operation, "NONE", first),
1025 SegmentationFilterCriteria.GenerateFilterCriteria(criteria.Field, criteria.Operation, "0", second),
1026 SegmentationFilterCriteria.GenerateFilterCriteria(criteria.Field, criteria.Operation, "", third),
1027 });
1028 if (criteria.Operation.Equals("notequal", StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase))
1029 {
1030 segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator = segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator.ReplaceJoinOperatorValue(criteria.Row, "((" + first + ")&(" + second + ")&(" + third + "))");
1031 }
1032 else
1033 {
1034 segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator = segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator.ReplaceJoinOperatorValue(criteria.Row, "((" + first + ")|(" + second + ")|(" + third + "))");
1035 }
1036 }
1037 else
1038 {
1039 var first = segmentationFilter.GetHighestRow();
1040
1041 criteriasForAdd.AddRange(new List<SegmentationFilterCriteria>
1042 {
1043 SegmentationFilterCriteria.GenerateFilterCriteria(criteria.Field, criteria.Operation , "NONE" , first)
1044 });
1045 segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator = segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator.ReplaceJoinOperatorValue(criteria.Row, "((" + first + "))");
1046 }
1047 }

1049 _ = segmentationFilter.Criterias.RemoveAll(x => x.Field.Equals("state", StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase) && x.Value.Equals("none", StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase));
1050 segmentationFilter.Criterias.AddRange(criteriasForAdd);
1051
1052 return segmentationFilter;
1053 }
1054
1055 public static SegmentationFilter SetDateFields(this SegmentationFilter segmentationFilter)
1056 {
1057 // TODO: Remove/simplify try/catch block
1058 try
1059 {
1060 var criteriasForAdd = new List<SegmentationFilterCriteria>();
1061 foreach (var criteria in segmentationFilter.Criterias.Where(x => x.Field.ToLower() is "clientstart" or "birthdate" or "anniversary"))
1062 {
1063 int rowFrom = segmentationFilter.GetHighestRow(), rowTo = rowFrom + 1;
1064 if (criteria.Operation == "Equal")
1065 {
1066 criteriasForAdd.AddRange(new List<SegmentationFilterCriteria>
1067 {
1068 SegmentationFilterCriteria.GenerateFilterCriteria(criteria.Field, "From", criteria.Value.SetTimeOffset().AddYears(-1).ToString(), rowFrom ),
1069 SegmentationFilterCriteria.GenerateFilterCriteria(criteria.Field, "To" , criteria.Value.SetTimeOffset().ToString(), rowTo)
1070 });
1071 segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator = segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator.ReplaceJoinOperatorValue(criteria.Row, "((" + rowFrom + ")&(" + rowTo + "))");
1072 }
1073 else
1074 {
1075 criteria.Value = criteria.Value.SetTimeOffset().ToString();
1076 criteriasForAdd.Add(criteria);
1077 }
1078 }
1079
1080 _ = segmentationFilter.Criterias.RemoveAll(x => x.Field.ToLower() is "clientstart" or "birthdate" or "anniversary");
1081 segmentationFilter.Criterias.AddRange(criteriasForAdd);
1082 }
1083 catch (Exception)
1084 {
1085 // When we want to download the list of recipients, it is not necessary to set timeoffset, ie. conversion of age to date range.
1086 // In this case criteria.Value.SetTimeOffset() raise exception becouse criteria.Value has DateTime string instead of an integer string.
1087 // We just keep going and return original segmentationFilter
1088 }
1089
1090 return segmentationFilter;
1091 }
1092
1093 public static SegmentationFilter SetTagsField(this SegmentationFilter segmentationFilter)
1094 {
1095 var criteriasForAdd = new List<SegmentationFilterCriteria>();
1096 foreach (var criteria in segmentationFilter.Criterias.Where(x => x.Field.Equals("tags", StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase)))
1097 {
1098 int rowFirst = segmentationFilter.GetHighestRow(criteriasForAdd.GetHighestRow()), rowSecond = rowFirst + 1, rowThird = rowSecond + 1, rowFourth = rowThird + 1;
1099 if (criteria.Operation.ToLower() is "equal" or "in")
1100 {
1101 criteriasForAdd.AddRange(new List<SegmentationFilterCriteria>
1102 {
1103 SegmentationFilterCriteria.GenerateFilterCriteria(criteria.Field, "Equal", criteria.Value, rowFirst ),
1104 SegmentationFilterCriteria.GenerateFilterCriteria(criteria.Field, "StartsWith" , criteria.Value + ";", rowSecond ),
1105 SegmentationFilterCriteria.GenerateFilterCriteria(criteria.Field, "EndsWith" , ";" + criteria.Value, rowThird ),
1106 SegmentationFilterCriteria.GenerateFilterCriteria(criteria.Field, "Contains" , ";" + criteria.Value + ";", rowFourth)
1107 });
1108 segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator = segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator.ReplaceJoinOperatorValue(criteria.Row, "((" + rowFirst + ")|(" + rowSecond + ")|(" + rowThird + ")|(" + rowFourth + "))");
1109 }
1110 else
1111 {
1112 // criteria.Operation.ToLower() == "contains" || criteria.Operation.ToLower() == "notcontains"
1113 criteriasForAdd.AddRange(new List<SegmentationFilterCriteria>
1114 {
1115 SegmentationFilterCriteria.GenerateFilterCriteria(criteria.Field, criteria.Operation, criteria.Value, rowFirst )
1116 });
1117 segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator = segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator.ReplaceJoinOperatorValue(criteria.Row, "((" + rowFirst + "))");
1118 }
1119 }
1120
1121 _ = segmentationFilter.Criterias.RemoveAll(x => x.Field.Equals("tags", StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase));
1122 segmentationFilter.Criterias.AddRange(criteriasForAdd);
1123 return segmentationFilter;
1124 }

1126 public static SegmentationFilter UpdateRowNumbers(this SegmentationFilter segmentationFilter, int highestRow)
1127 {
1128 foreach (var criteria in segmentationFilter.Criterias.OrderByDescending(x => x.Row))
1129 {
1130 var newRowValue = criteria.Row + highestRow;
1131 segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator = segmentationFilter.CriteriaJoinOperator.Replace("(" + criteria.Row + ")", "(" + newRowValue + ")");
1132 criteria.Row = newRowValue;
1133 }
1134
1135 return segmentationFilter;
1136 }

1138 public static SegmentationFilter RemoveGroupCriteria(this SegmentationFilter segmentationFilter, bool isThirdLevel = false)

1145 }

1148 }

1150 return segmentationFilter;
